OL,3,CJapanese man acquitted of murder after
OL,4,Cspending 46 years on death row
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Neil Connery
OL,7,Freports on the acquittal of the
OL,8,Fworld's longest death row prisoner
OL,10,FA Japanese court has ruled that an 88-
OL,11,Fyear-old former boxer was not guilty
OL,12,Fin a retrial for a 1966 quadruple
OL,13,Fmurder, reversing an earlier wrongful
OL,14,Fconviction after decades on death row.
