OL,3,CJapanese man acquitted of murder after
OL,4,Cspending 46 years on death row
OL,6,FIwao Hakamada's acquittal by the
OL,7,FShizuoka District Court makes him the
OL,8,Ffifth death-row convict to be found
OL,9,Fnot guilty in a retrial in postwar
OL,10,FJapanese criminal justice. The case
OL,11,Fcould rekindle a debate around
OL,12,Fabolishing the death penalty in Japan.
OL,14,FThe court's presiding judge, Koshi
OL,15,FKunii, said the court acknowledged a
OL,16,Fmultiple fabrications of evidence and
OL,17,Fthat Hakamada was not the culprit, NHK
OL,18,Fsaid.
