OL,3,CJapanese man acquitted of murder after
OL,4,Cspending 46 years on death row
OL,6,FIt took 27 years for the top court to
OL,7,Fdeny his first appeal for retrial. His
OL,8,Fsecond appeal for a retrial was filed
OL,9,Fin 2008 by his sister Hideko Hakamada,
OL,10,Fnow 91, and the court finally ruled in
OL,11,Fhis favor in 2023, paving the way for
OL,12,Fthe latest retrial that began in
OL,13,FOctober.
