OL,3,CJapanese man acquitted of murder after
OL,4,Cspending 46 years on death row
OL,6,FHakamada was released from prison in
OL,7,F2014 when a court ordered a retrial
OL,8,Fbased on new evidence suggesting his
OL,9,Fconviction may have been based on
OL,10,Ffabricated accusations by
OL,11,Finvestigators, but was not cleared of
OL,12,Fthe conviction. After his release,
OL,13,FHakamada served his sentence at home
OL,14,Fbecause his frail health and age made
OL,15,Fhim a low risk for escape.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
