OL,6,FAt a final hearing at the Shizuoka
OL,7,Fcourt in May before Thursday's
OL,8,Fdecision, prosecutors again demanded
OL,9,Fthe death penalty, triggering
OL,10,Fcriticism from rights groups that
OL,11,Fprosecutors were trying to prolong the
OL,12,Ftrial.
