OL,3,CJapanese man acquitted of murder after
OL,4,Cspending 46 years on death row
OL,6,FThe extremely high hurdles for
OL,7,Fretrials have also prompted legal
OL,8,Fexperts to call for a revision to the
OL,9,Fsystem.
OL,11,FDuring the investigation that followed
OL,12,Fhis arrest, Hakamada initially denied
OL,13,Fthe accusations, then confessed. He
OL,14,Flater said he was forced to confess
OL,15,Funder violent interrogation by police.
