OL,3,CJapanese man acquitted of murder after
OL,4,Cspending 46 years on death row
OL,6,FA major point of contention was five
OL,7,Fpieces of blood-stained clothing that
OL,8,Finvestigators claimed Hakamada wore
OL,9,Fduring the crime and hid in a tank of
OL,10,Ffermented soybean paste, or miso. The
OL,11,Fclothes were found more than a year
OL,12,Fafter his arrest.
OL,14,FA Tokyo High Court ruling in 2023
OL,15,Facknowledged scientific experiments
OL,16,Fthat clothing soaked in miso for more
OL,17,Fthan a year turns too dark for
OL,18,Fbloodstains to be spotted, noting a
OL,19,Fpossible fabrication by investigators.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
