OL,3,CJapanese man acquitted of murder after
OL,4,Cspending 46 years on death row
OL,6,FHis sister Hideko Hakamada has devoted
OL,7,Faround half of her life to win his
OL,8,Finnocence. Before Thursday's ruling,
OL,9,Fshe said she was in a never-ending
OL,10,Fbattle.
OL,12,F"It is so difficult to get a retrial
OL,13,Fstarted," She told reporters in Tokyo.
OL,14,F"Not just Iwao, but I'm sure there are
OL,15,Fother people who have been wrongly
OL,16,Faccused and crying. ... I want the
OL,17,Fcriminal law revised so that retrials
OL,18,Fare more easily available."
